WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:00.839
Qín Ruò Yǔ

2
00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:02.999
How dare you try to kill someone?

3
00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:04.439
Jiā Háo, listen to my explanation

4
00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:05.279
It wasn’t me

5
00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:09.919
Just wait to rot in prison

6
00:00:11.120 --> 00:00:11.639
Qín Ruò Yǔ

7
00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:13.239
You are now suspected of intentional murder

8
00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:14.359
Please come with us

9
00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:15.359
To undergo investigation

10
00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:17.279
I didn’t do it, I didn’t!

11
00:00:30.520 --> 00:00:31.559
Young Master, you called for me?

12
00:00:31.880 --> 00:00:32.439
It’s been half a month

13
00:00:32.440 --> 00:00:33.559
I haven’t been able to contact Ruò Yǔ

14
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:35.599
Go find her

15
00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:37.559
At all costs, you must find her

16
00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:38.479
Yes

17
00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:45.319
Isn’t this

18
00:00:45.320 --> 00:00:47.239
The CEO Qín who once dominated Dōng Hǎi?

19
00:00:48.560 --> 00:00:49.079
What’s wrong?

20
00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:51.439
In less than a month

21
00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:53.279
You’ve fallen into such a miserable state

22
00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:55.759
Why are you here?

23
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.199
Shouldn’t you be in the hospital?

24
00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:01.399
Are you okay?

25
00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:03.919
Of course I’m fine

26
00:01:04.120 --> 00:01:05.359
If something happened to me

27
00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:06.759
How could I shine so brightly

28
00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:07.839
And marry Jiā Háo?

29
00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:09.959
Let me tell you the truth

30
00:01:10.160 --> 00:01:12.039
Everything you’re going through now

31
00:01:12.680 --> 00:01:14.519
Was all planned by me and Jiā Háo

32
00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:17.239
Right, Jiā Háo?